(1, 'The Galaxy S8 Plus is an ergonomic marvel', 1, '2017-05-12 20:28:03', ' <div class=\"l-col__main\">\r\n    <figure class=\"e-image e-image--hero\">\r\n  <span class=\"e-image__inner\">\r\n    <span class=\"e-image__image \" data-original=\"https://cdn0.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/54336475/vsavov_170419_1624_0001_2.0.jpg\">   \r\n        <picture class=\"c-picture\" data-cid=\"site/picture_element-1492622054_9470_6089\" data-cdata=\"{&quot;picture&quot;:true,&quot;dynamic_picture&quot;:false,&quot;convert_picture&quot;:false}\">\r\n    <source srcset=\"https://cdn0.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/UobCcFC1yd64uIDnEOCeKuhLWMs=/0x0:2040x1360/320x213/filters:focal(708x496:1034x822):format(webp)/cdn0.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/54336475/vsavov_170419_1624_0001_2.0.jpg 320w, https://cdn0.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/HutdzD4WBAtbbuq1jsIK07QsKLY=/0x0:2040x1360/420x280/filters:focal(708x496:1034x822):format(webp)/cdn0.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/54336475/vsavov_170419_1624_0001_2.0.jpg 420w, https://cdn0.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Qsx54VlbTyo6vxnKJHN36KNelBA=/0x0:2040x1360/520x347/filters:focal(708x496:1034x822):format(webp)/cdn0.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/54336475/vsavov_170419_1624_0001_2.0.jpg 520w, https://cdn0.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0YPH_kpqxHs2WNS5MxqYsakmXiI=/0x0:2040x1360/620x413/filters:focal(708x496:1034x822):format(webp)/cdn0.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/54336475/vsavov_170419_1624_0001_2.0.jpg 620w, https://cdn0.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/x6tY3KJX_IO9nipcpq6kLHQiW24=/0x0:2040x1360/720x480/filters:focal(708x496:1034x822):format(webp)/cdn0.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/54336475/vsavov_170419_1624_0001_2.0.jpg 720w, https://cdn0.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/PrUSGU0l0Yx2Vzm9KbT6ymAK5dM=/0x0:2040x1360/820x547/filters:focal(708x496:1034x822):format(webp)/cdn0.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/54336475/vsavov_170419_1624_0001_2.0.jpg 820w, https://cdn0.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/3aUucRVYCJtTgaM_Dfx64RYRqZ4=/0x0:2040x1360/920x613/filters:focal(708x496: