(10, 'Ransomware explained: Hacking for cash threats on the rise', 4, '2017-05-14 22:02:39', '<div class=\"sdc-article-widget sdc-article-image\">\r\n          <figure class=\"sdc-article-image__figure\" itemprop=\"associatedMedia image\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\">\r\n            <div class=\"sdc-article-image__wrapper\" data-aspect-ratio=\"16/9\">\r\n                <img class=\"sdc-article-image__item   \" itemprop=\"contentUrl\" src=\"http://e3.365dm.com/17/02/1096x616/5be3139202a5c2c083020780d7f8c7a6ab1c189d2ba6ae905e8eb27ff25a2598_3887199.jpg?20170208150710\" srcset=\"   http://e3.365dm.com/17/02/320x180/5be3139202a5c2c083020780d7f8c7a6ab1c189d2ba6ae905e8eb27ff25a2598_3887199.jpg?20170208150710 320w,    http://e3.365dm.com/17/02/640x380/5be3139202a5c2c083020780d7f8c7a6ab1c189d2ba6ae905e8eb27ff25a2598_3887199.jpg?20170208150710 640w,    http://e3.365dm.com/17/02/736x414/5be3139202a5c2c083020780d7f8c7a6ab1c189d2ba6ae905e8eb27ff25a2598_3887199.jpg?20170208150710 736w,    http://e3.365dm.com/17/02/1096x616/5be3139202a5c2c083020780d7f8c7a6ab1c189d2ba6ae905e8eb27ff25a2598_3887199.jpg?20170208150710 1096w,    http://e3.365dm.com/17/02/1600x900/5be3139202a5c2c083020780d7f8c7a6ab1c189d2ba6ae905e8eb27ff25a2598_3887199.jpg?20170208150710 1600w,    http://e3.365dm.com/17/02/1920x1080/5be3139202a5c2c083020780d7f8c7a6ab1c189d2ba6ae905e8eb27ff25a2598_3887199.jpg?20170208150710 1920w,    http://e3.365dm.com/17/02/2048x1152/5be3139202a5c2c083020780d7f8c7a6ab1c189d2ba6ae905e8eb27ff25a2598_3887199.jpg?20170208150710 2048w\" alt=\"A picture taken on October 17, 2016 shows an employee walking behind a glass wall with machine coding symbols at the headquarters of Internet security giant Kaspersky in Moscow\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" title=\"A picture taken on October 17, 2016 shows an employee walking behind a glass wall with machine coding symbols at the headquarters of Internet security giant Kaspersky in Moscow\">\r\n            </div>\r\n              <figcaption class=\"sdc-article-image__caption\" itemprop=\"caption description\">\r\n                <span class=\"sdc-article-image__visually-hidden\">Image:</span>\r\n                <span class=\"sdc-article-image__caption-text\">Ransomware often infects a computer through an email attachment, link or fake software update</span>\r\n              </figcaption>\r\n          </figure>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        \r\n        \r\n        \r\n        \r\n\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"sdc-news-story-article\">\r\n        \r\n                    <p class=\"sdc-news-story-article__byline\">By Daniel Cairns, News Reporter</p>\r\n        \r\n                <p class=\"sdc-news-story-article__intro\">The NHS has been hit by a large ransomware cyberattack - but how do they work and how fast is the problem growing?</p>\r\n        \r\n            <div class=\"sdc-news-story-article__body\">\r\n                <div class=\"ad ad--mpu-tablet\"><div class=\"sdc-site-au \" data-ad-format=\"mpu\" data-type=\"\"><div class=\"sdc-site-au__mpu\" data-role=\"ad-container\" data-config=\"{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;mpu-inline&quot;,&quot;tag&quot;:&quot;20346936\\/skynews\\/tech\\/content&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:{&quot;mobile&quot;:[[300,250]],&quot;tablet&quot;:[[300,250]],&quot;desktop&quot;:[[300,250]]},&quot;targeting&quot;:{&quot;platform&quot;:&quot;live&quot;,&quot;artId&quot;:10874404}}\" data-targeting-strnativekey=\"\" data-targeting-platform=\"\" data-tag=\"\" data-component-name=\"sdc-site-mpu\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" id=\"mpu-inline\" data-tolerance=\"2\"></div></div>\r\n</div><p>Quite simply, ransomware locks or encrypts files or documents and demands payment to regain access.</p><p>The user is usually met with a basic screen that explains what is going on and instructions on how much and where to pay.</p><p>A countdown timer can threaten to delete - or expose the files publicly - if the ransom is not paid by a certain time.</p><p>Or - if the deadline is missed - the ransom sometimes increases.</p><p>However, even if payment is made there is no guarantee the files will be restored and some traces of the hostile programme could remain.</p><div class=\"sdc-article-widget sdc-article-image\">\r\n  <figure class=\"sdc-article-image__figure\" itemprop=\"associatedMedia image\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\">\r\n    <div class=\"sdc-article-image__wrapper\" data-aspect-ratio=\"4/3\">\r\n        <img class=\"sdc-article-image__item   \" itemprop=\"contentUrl\" src=\"http://e3.365dm.com/17/05/750x563/5bc0f1ff8c05adf644a5bead2bc8dbb911d585ebe6af12d65e6111490d6d17bd_3951787.jpg?20170512162023\" srcset=\"   http://e3.365dm.com/17/05/206x155/5bc0f1ff8c05adf644a5bead2bc8dbb911d585ebe6af12d65e6111490d6d17bd_3951787.jpg?20170512162023 206w,    http://e3.365dm.com/17/05/288x216/5bc0f1ff8c05adf644a5bead2bc8dbb911d585ebe6af12d65e6111490d6d17bd_3951787.jpg?20170512162023 288w,    http://e3.365dm.com/17/05/589x442/5bc0f1ff8c05adf644a5bead2bc8dbb911d585ebe6af12d65e6111490d6d17bd_3951787.jpg?20170512162023 589w,    http://e3.365dm.com/17/05/750x563/5bc0f1ff8c05adf644a5bead2bc8dbb911d585ebe6af12d65e6111490d6d17bd_3951787.jpg?20170512162023 750w\" alt=\"Hackers have attacked NHS computers\" title=\"Hackers have attacked NHS computers\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\">\r\n    </div>\r\n      <figcaption class=\"sdc-article-image__caption\" itemprop=\"caption description\">\r\n        <span class=\"sdc-article-image__visually-hidden\">Image:</span>\r\n        <span class=\"sdc-article-image__caption-text\">The NHS attack is typical and demands $300 in Bitcoin</span>\r\n      </figcaption>\r\n  </figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>The criminals usually demand payment in Bitcoin because the virtual currency is harder to trace.</p><p>Ransomware normally installs itself on a computer or phone via a Trojan programme disguised as something innocent, such as an email attachment/link, a popular app, or a fake software update.</p><p>NHS Digital said it was affected by WannaCry, also known as Wanna Decryptor, which experts describe as the \"atom bomb of ransomware\".</p><p>The flaw exploited by the programme was identified by the US National Security Agency, according to cybersecurity researcher Chris Doman.</p><p>He told Sky News that a hacking group called Shadow Brokers - believed to be Russian - then released documents to publicise the flaw.</p><p>\"It\'s called Eternal Blue - that\'s the codename - it was leaked about a month ago,\" said Mr Doman.</p><p>Cybersecurity experts agree the threat from Ransomware is growing at an alarming rate.</p><p>McAfee Labs said ransomware cases grew 80% in 2016.</p><div class=\"ad ad--mpu-mobile\"><div class=\"sdc-site-au \" data-ad-format=\"mpu\" data-type=\"\"><div class=\"sdc-site-au__mpu\" data-role=\"ad-container\" data-config=\"{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;mpu-inline-mobile&quot;,&quot;tag&quot;:&quot;20346936\\/skynews\\/tech\\/content&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:{&quot;mobile&quot;:[[300,250]],&quot;tablet&quot;:[[300,250]],&quot;desktop&quot;:[[300,250]]},&quot;targeting&quot;:{&quot;platform&quot;:&quot;live&quot;,&quot;artId&quot;:10874404}}\" data-targeting-strnativekey=\"\" data-targeting-platform=\"\" data-tag=\"\" data-component-name=\"sdc-site-mpu\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" id=\"mpu-inline-mobile\" data-tolerance=\"2\"></div></div>\r\n</div><p>Fellow anti-virus firm Malwarebytes reported that 40% of the 540 businesses it surveyed last year had been affected, with some criminals demanding more than $50,000.</p><p>Ransomware was also in almost 40% of spam email in 2016, according to an IBM Security study.</p> <div class=\"sdc-article-widget sdc-article-image\">\r\n  <figure class=\"sdc-article-image__figure\" itemprop=\"associatedMedia image\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\">\r\n    <div class=\"sdc-article-image__wrapper\" data-aspect-ratio=\"4/3\">\r\n        <img class=\"sdc-article-image__item   \" itemprop=\"contentUrl\" src=\"http://e3.365dm.com/17/05/750x563/37d35f0951b4389d2a01ba526979126414242fbc0e963e25689f9c57632d45e2_3951895.jpg?20170512184931\" srcset=\"   http://e3.365dm.com/17/05/206x155/37d35f0951b4389d2a01ba526979126414242fbc0e963e25689f9c57632d45e2_3951895.jpg?20170512184931 206w,    http://e3.365dm.com/17/05/288x216/37d35f0951b4389d2a01ba526979126414242fbc0e963e25689f9c57632d45e2_3951895.jpg?20170512184931 288w,    http://e3.365dm.com/17/05/589x442/37d35f0951b4389d2a01ba526979126414242fbc0e963e25689f9c57632d45e2_3951895.jpg?20170512184931 589w,    http://e3.365dm.com/17/05/750x563/37d35f0951b4389d2a01ba526979126414242fbc0e963e25689f9c57632d45e2_3951895.jpg?20170512184931 750w\" alt=\"Hackers attacked San Francisco&amp;#39;s light rail system with ransomware in November 2016 \" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" title=\"Hackers attacked San Francisco&amp;#39;s light rail system with ransomware in November 2016 \">\r\n    </div>\r\n      <figcaption class=\"sdc-article-image__caption\" itemprop=\"caption description\">\r\n        <span class=\"sdc-article-image__visually-hidden\">Image:</span>\r\n        <span class=\"sdc-article-image__caption-text\">Hackers attacked San Francisco\'s light rail system with ransomware in November 2016 </span>\r\n      </figcaption>\r\n  </figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>San Francisco\'s light rail system was one recent high-profile victim.</p><p>It was held ransom in November 2016, with ticket machines taken down and the city forced to open the gates and let passengers travel for free.</p><p>The attacker reportedly demanded $70,000 to get things back up and running - but the company said it refused to pay and sorted the problem itself.</p><p>As well as being careful what you open and being sure of the source, keeping a physically separate back-up of data, such as on an external hard drive, is one way to mitigate the effects of a ransomware attack.</p><p>Good anti-virus software is also recommended.</p><p>Pete Turner, from security company Avast, told Sky News his firm had seen a 100% year-on-year increase.</p> <div class=\"sdc-article-widget sdc-article-image\">\r\n  <figure class=\"sdc-article-image__figure\" itemprop=\"associatedMedia image\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\">\r\n    <div class=\"sdc-article-image__wrapper\" data-aspect-ratio=\"4/3\">\r\n        <img class=\"sdc-article-image__item   \" itemprop=\"contentUrl\" src=\"http://e3.365dm.com/17/03/750x563/a25172b0007e734af1d783945400f3a8710c78b75ec3351110b4a9c824d49aab_3919039.jpg?20170329033821\" srcset=\"   http://e3.365dm.com/17/03/206x155/a25172b0007e734af1d783945400f3a8710c78b75ec3351110b4a9c824d49aab_3919039.jpg?20170329033821 206w,    http://e3.365dm.com/17/03/288x216/a25172b0007e734af1d783945400f3a8710c78b75ec3351110b4a9c824d49aab_3919039.jpg?20170329033821 288w,    http://e3.365dm.com/17/03/589x442/a25172b0007e734af1d783945400f3a8710c78b75ec3351110b4a9c824d49aab_3919039.jpg?20170329033821 589w,    http://e3.365dm.com/17/03/750x563/a25172b0007e734af1d783945400f3a8710c78b75ec3351110b4a9c824d49aab_3919039.jpg?20170329033821 750w\" alt=\"The Samsung Galaxy S7 was unveiled in February 2016\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" title=\"The Samsung Galaxy S7 was unveiled in February 2016\">\r\n    </div>\r\n      <figcaption class=\"sdc-article-image__caption\" itemprop=\"caption description\">\r\n        <span class=\"sdc-article-image__visually-hidden\">Image:</span>\r\n        <span class=\"sdc-article-image__caption-text\">Ransomware can also get onto a phone if a user downloads an unverified app</span>\r\n      </figcaption>\r\n  </figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\"These things are often caused by the weakest thing in the security chain - us,\" he said.</p><p>\"It\'s easy to fall into a trap, to click on a link in an email, go to a website we shouldn\'t, to download a bit of software attached to an email. And all of a sudden, our computer is locked completely.</p><p>\"It\'s not just businesses, it\'s us individuals as well.\"</p><p>Its report in March said: \"Ransomware on connected watches, fitness trackers and TVs will present a challenge to manufacturers, and it is not yet known whether customer support will extend to assisting with unlocking devices and providing advice on whether to pay a ransom.\"</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        \r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n            <div class=\"sdc-site-outbrain sdc-site-outbrain--AR_3\">\r\n                <div class=\"OUTBRAIN\" data-src=\"http://news.sky.com/story/hacking-for-cash-ransomware-threats-on-the-rise-10874404\" data-widget-id=\"AR_3\" data-ob-template=\"skynews\"></div>\r\n                <script src=\"//widgets.outbrain.com/outbrain.js\" async=\"true\"></script>\r\n            </div>', 4, 'Images/stream7.jpg', 1);

